{{Image}}
The '''CNS Strength Enhancer''' was an experimental system that amplified power signals along the lengths of the central [[nervous system]]. This generator, attached to a belt, provided greater impulses to all muscles, as well as a resistance to all sorts of perturbations of the user's system.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]'' {{1st}}
